{"tid":496717,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"KOL獅子開大口態度差","createTime":"2017-12-12T03:34:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T11:22:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e75fca6fa79db2e97a6d0743ecdff90a8c421235","tid":496717,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:34:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171212/20241927\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171212%2F20241927&d=Yt7A02elDoz4Cy37BAznhxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=0d37a0a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171212%2F20241927&h=a3f4be49\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171212/20241927</a><br />\n<br />\nKOL獅子開大口態度差<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】近年KOL（Key Opinion Leader、關鍵意見領袖）氾濫，facebook專頁有數萬個like就可自稱KOL接廣告，收數千至數萬元出一個post。由普通人搖身一變成為廣告界新寵，當中難免良莠不齊，有廣告人就力數KOL三宗罪，「獅子開大口、態度差、唔專業」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171212/large/a0403a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171212%2Flarge%2Fa0403a.gif&h=ed45f63c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n笑波子(左三)早前與正義聯盟主角拍的宣傳片遭網民批評。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n笑波子英文「小學雞」<br />\n<br />\n有不願開名的廣告人指，近年所謂的KOL部份只不過是一班King of Like，在社交平台上有較多人關注，方便落廣告，很多時根本談不上是意見領袖。他指，不少品牌一開始時喜歡用KOL，「一來有新鮮感，二來較明星平」，但當人人都自稱KOL的時代，少不免出現樹大有枯枝的情況。<br />\n<br />\n「有好多唔算係好出名嘅KOL，開價同電視台明星仔一樣，工作態度又差，遲到又唔記稿，以為自己係大明星，咁我點解唔搵返電視台，至少訓練過又聽話」，故不少「KOL」一段時間過後就再接不到工作，消失於人前。<br />\n<br />\n以坐擁數十萬訂閱的Youtuber笑波子為例，早前一條與正義聯盟主角會面的宣傳片便被網民批評，指其不專業以及英文「小學雞」。當然，KOL 當中仍有人保持態度好、長做長有，更可入屋上電視。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁偉聰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t廣告季袋790億　佔收入98%<br />\n要聞 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t電視台變陣搶廣告見效<br />\n要聞 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t不滿壟斷　網絡作家「移民」 Medium<br />\n要聞 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t「唔畀錢　產品冇人見到」受制網絡霸權焗進貢廣告界：幫fb打工<br />\n要聞 5小時前"},{"pid":"074bf56a159b51c301364835899b1c4cbef5bea2","tid":496717,"uid":38671,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:37:37.000Z","msg":"傻既先搵呢班kol落廣告<br />\n根本只係班小學雞偶像<br />\n出到街無人識"},{"pid":"e0a7a27cd8f9e5edbd1787a4cba25ab2f38d93ae","tid":496717,"uid":31228,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:40:12.000Z","msg":"瓊狗咪係囉 仲要成日上黎抄Post"},{"pid":"a6c8e511ae179faecb891a3c3dca991f1db35dee","tid":496717,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:41:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>瓊狗咪係囉 仲要成日上黎抄Post</blockquote><br />\n佢好彩食左第一水"},{"pid":"14896b200bdc970a942b3009020ec3583dd880fc","tid":496717,"uid":31228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:56:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>瓊狗咪係囉 仲要成日上黎抄Post</blockquote><br />\n佢好彩食左第一水</blockquote><br />\n之前個D韓文歌屌屌屌咪係囉 FB仲一大班CM添<br />\n睇KOL?不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242854ba917f192719727b1770c558265159be61","tid":496717,"uid":43173,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T04:37:59.000Z","msg":"點可以話樹大有枯枝，根本成棵都係枯樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd28ca44193150330a7be4a5bf5753bb8d1958f","tid":496717,"uid":86408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T05:48:47.000Z","msg":"墨屎仔唔係有好多小學雞fans咩 ??無人護主既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"558151bf93e6044cdfd63bafaf5cde2cf9821bc4","tid":496717,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T05:49:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>墨屎仔唔係有好多小學雞fans咩 ??無人護主既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢班fans年齡層仲低過連登仔"},{"pid":"b63a98d91be139b82e7a4fdda6a1b1375ed30b58","tid":496717,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite